# The repo-root .gitignore has a global `*.mp3`; re-include the demo's generated speech
# clips so the video is reproducible (and the committed mp4 has its source audio).
!public/*.mp3

# The rendered demo (out/yarnia-demo.mp4) IS tracked on purpose so the demo video
# ships with the repo. Re-render with: npx remotion render YarniaDemo out/yarnia-demo.mp4
